    • addDatabase

      public javax.ws.rs.core.Response addDatabase(String databaseKey, SQLDatabaseType databaseTypeCode, String username, String password, String database, String host, Integer port, VisualizationType visualizationTypeIndex)
      Adds a sql database to the users available/usable databases (via the sqldatabase manager).
      Parameters:
      databaseKey - key which is later used to identify the database
      databaseTypeCode - type of the database (DB2, MySql, ...)
      username - the username for the database
      password - the password for the database
      database - the name of the database
      host - the database address
      port - the database port
      visualizationTypeIndex - encoding of the returned message
      Returns:
      success or error message, if possible in the requested encoding/format
